highlights.text: “Say You Won't Let Go” by James Arthur has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 77 weeks straight.
“Rise” by Jonas Blue and Jack & Jack is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 99 spots at #101.
“Reborn” by KIDS SEE GHOSTS is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #21.
Post Malone has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Better Now” is the highest at #1.
